Interface SendQueue<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Output
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicSendQueue

    public interface SendQueue<T>
extends Output
    This provides a non-thread safe access to an output queue which allows batching of messages to other threads to minimize thread coordination.

    Created by Richard on 7/18/14.
